author: COMSOL
description:
A solution is pumped through a catalytic bed where a solute species reacts as it gets in contact with the catalyst. For a given total pressure difference across the bed, this model finds the optimal catalyst distribution to maximize the total reaction rate of the solute.

The model requires the Optimization Module.
label: microreactor_optimization.mph
